title: Armitron Presents: Andrea Ager of Team Dynamix on Motivation
description: CrossFit Athlete and Team Dynamix member, Andrea Ager, talks about the small details that can make a big impact on your fitness, your attitude and your life.

transcripts: It's hard for people to wake up at six am and go to the gym and do everything that is asked of us. And in Colosenses 3:23 is one of my favorite scripture verses it just says 'In Everything you do , do it with all your heart, working for the Lord and not for mankind." And that means so much to me on so many different levels because it means that no task is to small and nothing is given to us without um looking back to God knowing that it was a gift.
